title: Ore wo Suki Nano wa Omae Dake ka yo
description: Question: What would you do, if a girl you’re interested would confess to you? On top of it, it wouldn’t be just the on girl. A cool upperclassman adored by the whole school. And your cheerful, energetic childhood friend. I bet you would be over the moon. Thing is, what if there was an unexpected problem about the contents of that confession?
artist: Ijima Yuu, Ijima yuuOre wo suki nano wa omae dake ka yo 39, ijima yuu
author: Rakuda (駱駝), Rakuda (らくだ)
